<p>An extremely long article but one worth the time to read as it contains an accurate picture of the US today in money terms, and, if I read it correctly, it says that the US has no way out of it&#8217;s dilemma that does not destroy the country. I saw this years ago, but he has put it into words and given reasons for each scenario. </p>
<p>This should be required reading for all of the sheeple, but most would get to paragraph two and lose interest. So be it. Those who read all of it will work to prepare for the day it all happens. I doubt we have too many years to do so.</p>
